&lt;p&gt;The Bristol Eye Hospital is looking to recruit a full time Permeant Receptionist/Clerical Officer to work within the busy Reception at BEH and Filton covering the reception desk booking in patients and process appointments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to have good attention to detail and IT skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a an exciting time to join our Reception team, we have various vacancies Full Time, Part Time Permeant and Fixed Term.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Any NHS or a healthcare environment experience would also be an advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to the very large responses we receive for jobs we are unable to respond to all candidates individually at application stage. Therefore, if you have not heard from us, you have regretfully been unsuccessful on this occasion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
